export const BookmarkIcon = (props: any) => {

        </svg>
    } else {
        return <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.394" height="27.009" viewBox="0 0 17.394 27.009">
            <path id="bookmark" d="M109.255,0h-10.6A2.649,2.649,0,0,0,96.01,2.649V24.9a.53.53,0,0,0,.9.375l7.042-7.043L111,25.275a.53.53,0,0,0,.9-.374V2.649A2.649,2.649,0,0,0,109.255,0Z" transform="translate(-95.26 0.75)" fill="none" stroke="#0a84ff" strokeWidth="1.5" />

    }


}
